The paper discusses the challenges and countermeasures related to botnets and their use of encrypted and covert DNS queries. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of algorithms and traffic analysis, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the challenges of detecting and blocking these queries, which could fall under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC).
